{"tid":775645,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李柱銘：「本土化」是錯誤的做法，不應視來港生活的大陸人為敵人","createTime":"2018-08-11T10:21:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T13:47:11.000Z","uid":70063,"like":4,"dislike":158,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"d116d67cdf79c134b1ccd0d2a973f142ea91b4b2","tid":775645,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:21:43.000Z","msg":"民主黨創黨主席、資深大律師李柱銘表示，香港人要堅守核心價值，又認為「本土化」是錯誤的做法。他解釋，大陸人來港定居某程度上是因為喜歡香港的生活方式，港人不應該視來港生活的大陸人為敵人，應該將香港的核心價值灌輸給他們。<br />\n<br />\n李柱銘出席講座時又說，每天有150個單程證名額，他們住滿7年便可成為選民，回歸以來已經累積大批從大陸來港人士成為選民，但現時立法會選舉民主派與建制派的得票，仍然維持大約六四比例，反映有部分大陸來港人士認同香港的核心價值，投票支持民主派。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1411869-20180811.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1411869-20180811.htm&d=O%2F0Z4sTj8nH98eKxysC4YOPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=8a52f23e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1411869-20180811.htm&h=1b4e02d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1411869-20180811.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c4416917be3dde4d5ddc16a588b874abc3cc5a19","tid":775645,"uid":42820,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:23:27.000Z","msg":"2018年都仲講緊呢D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ceac8233f88e4159f5de3abc8ff85e214e7009d","tid":775645,"uid":895,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:24:40.000Z","msg":"天真過天真嬌"},{"pid":"9f7b3ad4ef175ebe14a28aff6ed69c86970b52f0","tid":775645,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:25:54.000Z","msg":"司徒華2.0"},{"pid":"cfc3b2fe4d3166b3da2aad9ed6ba17a365e4b674","tid":775645,"uid":62815,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:26:46.000Z","msg":"但係人地目的係掠奪你一切嘛<br />\n咪咁左膠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/f